  <text x="20" y="48" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">Variationskoeffizient (Standardabw. ÷ Mittelwert) von Samuelsons Wette (Gewinn +200 $ / Verlust -100 $, je 50%)</text>
  <text x="20" y="86" fill="#d4d4d8" font-size="13.5" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">N=1</text>
  <rect x="170" y="74" width="400" height="22" fill="#f59e0b" rx="3"/>
